    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_f780fef7"><bpmn:text>Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. a&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. b&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. c&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. d&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. e&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_b2a71d9d"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_af0f1205"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 18 Abs. 1, point 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_df2a7518"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_fdd27ada"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_273c2ad1"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Legitimate Interest AND High Risk to Individuals AND Risk to Rights & Freedoms AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_c637df85"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Direct Marketing AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_55c88f4c"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Public Interest Processing AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_f67e882d"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 18 Abs. 1, point 2&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Processing Was Lawful</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_8b99133c"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_188f2a33"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Original Consent Given AND Data Subject Gave Consent</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_ff70e12e"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Use reasonable effort&#10;Applies when: Information Made Public</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
